and downs for the risk</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/83520896/image_83520896.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742632-schd-is-a-tech-light-dividend-etf-that-can-punch-above-its-weight", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 18:24:48"}, {"id": "4742631", "title": "Luk Fook: Harvesting My Losses (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lukfook Jewellery Sign\" data-id=\"458682413\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458682413/image_458682413.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">tanukiphoto/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December is a peak time for tax-loss harvesting, an activity I've increasin